 by +yyyy.<br/><br/>Just remember, the Blood Reaver has gotten me 10 times in 2 days... and most of the time, I didn't even have time for a screenshot, if I saw it at all.  <br/><br/>Sagonene<br/>Red Wolf Clan<br/>35th Magician<br/>Zeb server<br/><br/>PS - Got all but the sash... have a 4 int belt.. NEVER going back until the Rathe Mountains Pizza delivery HG's come back :)</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
